mtx: invoke mtxrun scripts in ``command subcommand`` syntax

usage: $ mtx SCRIPTNAME [ ARG1, ARG2, ... ]

examples:

    mtx                                 mtxrun
    $ mtx fonts --statistics            $ mtxrun --script fonts --statistics
    $ mtx plain --make                  $ mtxrun --script plain --make
    $ mtx context somefile.tex          $ mtxrun --script context somefile.tex
                                    or: $ context somefile.tex
    $ mtx context --once somefile.tex   $ mtxrun --script context --once somefile.tex
    $ mtx cache --list                  $ mtxrun --script cache --list
    $ mtx grep mtx mtx                  $ mtxrun --script grep mtx mtx


